# ===================================================
# EA-NITI PRODUCTION GITIGNORE
# ===================================================

# --- [1] Dependencies & Builds ---
node_modules/
dist/
dist-ssr/
.vite/
*.local

# --- [2] AI Core Brain (REQUIRED FOR RUNTIME) ---
# We explicitly allow these compiled binaries so the agent functions.
!public/baseline_corpus.bin.gz
!public/baseline_meta.json
!public/lexicon.json

# --- [3] Raw Source Data (INTERNAL ONLY) ---
# Ignore the raw uncompressed CSVs/TXTs used to build the brain.
public/ee.csv
public/words.txt
public/EnterpriseArchitectureLearnings.txt
public/*.bin
*.gguf
*.onnx

# --- [4] Database, Cache & Traces ---
.cache/
*.idb
*.dexie
*.sqlite
*.tmp
trace_hydration.json.json.gz

# --- [5] Environment & Security (CRITICAL) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- [6] OS & IDE Junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.code-workspace

# --- [7] Internal Agent Metadata & Research ---
# These files contain internal developer instructions/IP.
.agents/
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
GEMINI.md
AGENTS.md
BIT_ARENA_LLD.md
PROJECT_STATUS.md
copilot-instructions.md
architecture.md
features.md
miner.ps1

# --- [8] Build, Test & Debug Logs ---
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
coverage/
tsc_output.txt
eslint_out.json
int_res.txt
ts_errors.txt
src/__tests__/